comments: I thought the various colours & differing names for each shape made it that bit trickier.  I didn’t use any pen/paper to take notes.  I tried mentally to assign to the various shapes as the study progressed.  I found Wopise an interesting word which with the holed shape i found easier to assign.  Zeti word was assigned to the pointed star shape, I associated the letter Z as pointy which I tried to get correct with the pointy shaped colours
